I was looking around at jigsaw puzzle programs, trying to find one
that will let me print jigsaw puzzles, when I actually ran across one
that would create jigsaw puzzles for free.  So I decided to try it out
on a couple of my scenarios:

Scen 122 - http://www.cei.net/~dphofrules/glad/SCEN122.exe
Scen 151 - http://www.cei.net/~dphofrules/glad/SCEN151.exe

If you think that's Scen 151 is hard, I did one with Telvido's "The
Labryinth".  No comment about how easy it was to get confused with
that maze.
